{
  "name": "Dirt Late Model",
  "description": "Dirt track late model with gloss color body, reflective numbers, heavy mud spatter pattern, and tread-marked lower panels. Has the authentic Saturday-night-short-track look.",
  "author": "Shokker Paint Booth",
  "version": "6.2.0",
  "compatible_with": "dirt_late_model, street_stock, modified",
  "notes": "Mud pattern intensity can be turned way down (40-60) for a cleaner 'hot lap' look or cranked up (100) for mid-race carnage. Numbers zone uses chrome for that classic vinyl-on-dirt reflectivity.",
